Package: summarizetaskview
Type: Package
Title: Creates summaries of the packages in a task view
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Brian C. O'Meara
Maintainer: Brian C. O'Meara <omeara.brian@gmail.com>
Description: Task views contain useful compilations of R packages, but it can be hard to tell from them which are abandoned, whether they meet current practices, and so forth. This tests for that.
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Requires: goodpractice,
  crandb,
  cranlogs,
  ggplot2,
  lubridate,
  ctv,
  parallel,
  packagemetrics,
  devtools
Remotes: ropenscilabs/packagemetrics
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
